{
  "stem": "5970.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And she always smiled when she hit somebody, a real sadist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They were wearing riding boots and uniforms with a SS insignia, like the men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And they were in charge of the women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They herded us into this bath house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Cold water, as I said before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And everything that we possessed was left outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "We were just like that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And then we were given these striped dresses and clothes to wear, underwear and whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It was all taken from other prisoners that were killed before us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And it was laundered and given to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I can't remember delousing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Maybe there was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But we still came from home, so we were pretty clean at that stage.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "But they did spray us with some awful stuff and gave us these terrible uniform.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And they gave us canvas shoes with wooden soles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Now, that was a disaster because the snow used to stick to it and you couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "So it was murder.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "But that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And we were taken to a barrack, all of us, all the women and children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "There were still children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "My younger sister was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And some other women with children were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And the barracks were not too bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "There were wooden-- sort of-- I wouldn't call them beds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "They were planks.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "But it was reasonably clean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "And we had like straw mattresses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And we were given a blanket as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And there to meet us came a young woman who was in charge.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "She was what they called the block elder there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "She was in charge of that block.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And we met some other women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Now, I just want to describe to you Majdanek.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "At that stage, Majdanek was one of the extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "It was divided into five fields.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
